{
  "stem": "27507.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was screaming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was screaming for people to come down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was screaming for people to assemble.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was shouting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then people were all the time being kept, somehow terrorized.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then there was everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Once they were kept waiting-- but once they started moving, everything had to be done on the double.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had to run rather than walk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Or they had to walk very fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And people were beaten at the same time so that they would not even think about-- so there was a conscious policy of terror.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Some people were shot in front of others, and maybe children were killed in front of others so that there would be such policy of fear and terror that nobody would be even able to think of offering resistance.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I think that fear was everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I think that the fear was there during the action, even if you were hiding in the shop.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Even if there was not immediate danger at this moment, there was a real-- I mean, something that was not experienced in the ghetto beforehand, to such an extent.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was terrible deprivation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was terrible poverty, and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But the terror that was experienced now was not experienced before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was a child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I was not-- so the shop was, as I said, a German managed factory, a big factory with halls and halls full of machines.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this area where we were, that area was called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "That was a knitting factory, where they were doing things like socks, and gloves, and knitted wear, probably jumpers, and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So there were big halls full of machines, full of workers, and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And my father was then started working.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
